<h2 id="using-signup">Using signup</h2>

<p>Signup enables users to enter their email address to subscribe to notifications. Itâ€™s primarily used for email signups but could also be applied to other methods of communication.</p>

<p>It includes a heading that should clearly and concisely tell the user what they are signing up to.</p>

